OL,5, A senior Christian cleric in Lebanon   
OL,6, has called for Syrian refugees to be   
OL,7, deported from the country.             
OL,9,FPatriarch Bechara Boutros Al-Rai, who  
OL,10,Fheads the Maronite Church, made the    
OL,11,Fcall in his Easter service message.    
OL,13,FHe said Syrian refugees, thought to    
OL,14,Fnumber as many as 1.5 million, were    
OL,15,F"draining the state's resources".      
OL,17,FAn independent monitoring group, the   
OL,18,FSyrian Network for Human Rights,       
OL,19,Faccused him of using inflammatory      
OL,20,Fspeech against vulnerable people.      
